title: Happy About Knowing What to Expect in 2009: Business, Electronic
description:
Wouldn't it be great to have a good handle on what will happen this year to make sure you could plan around it? "Happy About Knowing What to Expect in 2009: Getting a Handle on the Year Ahead" provides a series of answers. For 2009, we have contributions from 75 executives with a number of interesting predictions.

Mitchell Levy has been making extremely accurate predictions since 1998. He was 85% accurate over the last couple of years. This book is a fun, entertaining and insightful read. You will be glad you spent the time and will be happy with you're new perspective.
